"Ibitangazamakuru , - in Kuri i AGAPANDE Ishusho Bya Amapaji Nyuma Amapaji "
"Yoherejwe: Kuri ikoresha Rimwe Bya i Ipaji: Umwirondoro: Indimi ( ) . "
"urusobe in Iburyo: , Na: , , A Ikomeye Disiki%1 na , na Kuri A net Na: Bya "
