"( /, , , ) Kuri A Dogere ( \" \" Kuva: &CUPS; ) . ni OYA A - Guhagarara - - "
"Abantu Ikindi &UNIX; ( nka * Cyangwa &MacOS; ) Gushaka Ibisobanuro: na . "

